        <title>Detecting Peaks</title>
        <content>
                <p>Once you are satisfied with the baseline for the chromatogram you can detect peaks in it.</p>
                <taskbox title="Steps to detect peaks">
                        <ol>
                                <li>Ensure that you are satisfied with the current baseline</li>
                                <li>Set your preferred settings in the "Processing"-pane of the inspector</li>
                                <li>Click on the "Detect Peaks" toolbar icon or choose the menu-item "Process" : "Detect Peaks"</li>
                        </ol>
                </taskbox>
